Broadstack,enables,developers,to,append,services,to,their,applications,by,creating,stacks,on,Broadstack,and,adding,one,click,add,ons,to,them,Broadstack,then,provides,a,webhook,containing,the,new,configuration,and,the,details,required,to,connect,the,application,to,the,add,ons,The,Broadstack,API,is,aimed,at,developers,who,have,provisioned,add,ons,It,allows,them,to,retrieve,a,list,of,stacks,that,have,installed,a,given,add,on,get,information,on,a,specific,stack,that,has,installed,an,add,on,and,update,the,config,variables,on,provisioned,resources